e="white-space: pre-wrap;">Categories of data subjects and personal data</span></li><li value="3" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Recipients of data</span></li><li value="4" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">International transfers</span></li><li value="5" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Time limits for deletion</span></li><li value="6" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Security measures in place</span></li></ul><h2 class="_editorHeading2_1knvi_84"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">11. Staff Training and Awareness</span></h2><ul class="_editorListUnordered_1knvi_131"><li value="1" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Regular data protection training for all staff</span></li><li value="2" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Specific training for those handling personal data</span></li><li value="3" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Awareness of individual responsibilities</span></li><li value="4" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Updates on legal and regulatory changes</span></li></ul><h2 class="_editorHeading2_1knvi_84"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">12. Third Party Processors</span></h2><p class="_editorParagraph_1knvi_66"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">When using third party processors:</span></p><ul class="_editorListUnordered_1knvi_131"><li value="1" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Written contracts with appropriate clauses</span></li><li value="2" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Due diligence on security measures</span></li><li value="3" class="_editorListItem_1knvi_145"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Regular monitoring and auditing</span></li><li value="4" class="_editorLis