plied under this Agreement.</span><br><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Assignment. The Consultant hereby assigns and, to the extent any such assignment cannot be made at present, hereby agrees to assign to the Company, without further compensation, all of his right, title and interest in and to all Concepts, Ideas, and Developments under this Agreement. The Consultant will execute all documents and perform all lawful acts which the Company considers necessary or advisable to secure its rights hereunder and to carry out the intent of this Agreement.</span><br><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">The parties have agreed that all exclusive intellectual property rights which will be created in the course of the performance by the Consultant of this Agreement, including those as provided Bern Convention on Protection of Works of Literature and Art ( Paris Act of 24.07.1971, as amended and restated on 02.10.1979), Universal Copyright Convention (1952), as well as other international legislative legal acts , in particular :</span><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">- right to use the object of intellectual property,</span><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">- exclusive right to allow the use of intellectual property,</span><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">- exclusive right to prevent illegal use of the intellectual property object , including prohibition thereof,</span><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">- and other rights both currently existing and which may exist in the future ,</span><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">shall be owned by the Company.</span></p><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">(g) The Companys exclusive property right to the objects of the intellectual property as created in course performance by the Consultant by this Agreement shall apply to both finished objects of intellectual property, and materials received when developing the same , relative derivative audio-visual reflections , notwithstanding the language and form of expression , including the initial text and objective code.</span></p><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">(h) The Consultant shall assist the Company and/or its designees in every proper way to secure the Companys rights in Inventions and related intellectual property rights in all countries. The Consultant shall execute all documents and other instruments that the Company deems necessary to apply for and obtain these rights and to assign to the Company the sole and exclusive rights , title , and interest in and to the Inventions , and any related intellectual property rights . The Consultants obligation to provide assistance shall continue after the termination or expiration of this Agreement. The Consultant shall not register or apply for registration , in his name or any third partys name , any intellectual property rights (in any country ) related to the inventions.</span></p><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><br><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">(i) The Consultant hereby transfers and assigns fully and irrevocably to the Company the exclusive proprietary rights therein ( including those owned jointly with third parties , if any, including without limitation (i) the right to use the inventions, (ii)the right to authorize the use of the inventions, (iii) the right to prevent ( prohibit) any improper or unauthorized use of the Inventions , and (iv) any other proprietary rights contemplated by applicable law.</span></p><h2 class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorHeading2" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">9 Headings</span></h2><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Headings and subheadings are for convenience only and shall not be deemed to be a part of this Agreement.</span></p><h2 class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorHeading2" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">10 Amendments</span></h2><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This Agreement may be amended or modified, in whole or in part, only by an instrument in writing signed by all parties hereto. Any amendment, consent, decision, waiver or other action to be made, taken or given by the Company with respect to the Agreement shall be made, taken or given on behalf of the Company.</span></p><h2 class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorHeading2" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">11 Notices</span></h2><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">All notices, requests, claims, demands and other communications under this Agreement shall be in writing or email and shall be deemed given if delivered personally or sent by overnight courier or email to the parties at the addresses (email) set forth below (or at such other address for a party as shall be specified by like notice, or email that parties usually use during providing of services).</span></p><h2 class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorHeading2" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">16 Counterparts</span></h2><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">This Agreement may be executed in two or more counterparts, each of which shall constitute an original and all of which shall be deemed a single agreement.</span></p><table class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTable" dir="ltr"><colgroup><col><col></colgroup><tbody><tr dir="ltr"><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="border: 1px solid black; width: 75px; vertical-align: top; text-align: start; background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245);"><h3 class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorHeading3" dir="ltr"><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;