c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTextBold" style="white-space: pre-wrap;"># of records</strong></b></p></th><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="width: 75px; background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245); border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top; text-align: start;"><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><b><strong class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTextBold" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">People Affected</strong></b></p></th><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="width: 75px; background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245); border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top; text-align: start;"><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><b><strong class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTextBold" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">System/Application/Database Involved</strong></b></p></th><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="width: 75px; background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245); border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top; text-align: start;"><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><b><strong class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTextBold" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Types of Data</strong></b></p></th><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="width: 75px; background-color: rgb(242, 243, 245); border: 1px solid black; vertical-align: top; text-align: start;"><p class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorParagraph" dir="ltr"><b><strong class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTextBold" style="white-space: pre-wrap;">Root Cause?</strong></b></p></th><th class="c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCell c1h__module__WysiwygEditor_editorTableCellHeader" dir="ltr" style="width: 75px; background-color: r